examples.en: I'm only claiming what is rightfully mine.
I'll return the money to its rightful owner.
He will be given his rightful place in the history books.
Surely they have a rightful claim on their father's land?
The property should be returned to its rightful owner.
George sat at the head of the table, in his rightful place as their leader.
Upon the restitution of the book to its rightful owner the child was given a tongue lashing.
